  "id": "mirai",
  "name": "Mirai",
  "title": "Sparkling Idol",
  "description": "It's not that Mirai doesn't like being an idol. In fact, singing is the greatest joy she has in life. She sang long before she was put on stage. She thought, in her early days at the academy, that if she worked hard enough, they would let her leave and travel the world. \n\nShe thought correctly. At ten years old, the Church began training her for the demanding lifestyle of an idol. She didn't mind the rigor, nor the invasion of her privacy. After all, her life was never really hers anyway. \n\nSometimes she wishes she could sing as herself, without using the Goddess's voice. Just once, to see if the people still love her. \n\nShe likes to think they would.",
